      "title": "Court bars anyone from moving close to Bandaranaike Statue",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Colombo Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage issued an order barring any faction from entering or gathering within a 50 meter radius of the Bandaranaike Statue located in Galle Face, Colombo.",
        "Sri Lanka Police told the court that there is a possible attempt being made to cause harm to the statue.",
        "IMF hopes to complete Sri Lanka aid talks \u2018as quickly as possible\u2019"
      ],
